    <item>
      <title>旅游业繁荣、芯片工厂推动日本土地价格创纪录增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/japan-roadside-land-prices-grow-most-on-record-on-tourism-semiconductors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本路边土地价值创下有史以来最大涨幅，这得益于该国旅游业蓬勃发展以及全球半导体供应链转变的地区。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/japan-roadside-land-prices-grow-most-on-record-on-tourism-semiconductors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 07:41:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡星展银行首次与稳定币合作，推动数字资产发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/dbs-bank-ties-up-with-paxos-in-first-stablecoin-custody-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡最大的银行星展集团控股有限公司将与加密货币发行商 Paxos Trust Co. 的本地子公司合作，首次托管稳定币储备并提供相关现金管理服务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/dbs-bank-ties-up-with-paxos-in-first-stablecoin-custody-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 07:07:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国著名大学濒临财务悬崖</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-07-02/uk-universities-dire-financial-straits-hit-by-immigration-limits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[学费上限和不断上升的通货膨胀迫使学校削减成本并招收更多有利可图的国际学生。这一策略现在与移民限制相冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2024-07-02/uk-universities-dire-financial-straits-hit-by-immigration-limits</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 04:01:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能的脑雾不会阻止对艺术的清算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-07-02/ai-is-failing-on-facts-but-crushing-it-on-creative-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[银行和医疗保健公司还需要几年时间才能解决人工智能的幻觉问题，但创意产业已经面临一些严重的破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-07-02/ai-is-failing-on-facts-but-crushing-it-on-creative-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 04:00:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国将通过新芯片法案工人计划解决劳动力短缺问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/us-to-fight-labor-shortage-with-new-chips-act-worker-program</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府正在启动一项培养美国计算机芯片劳动力的计划，旨在避免可能损害国内半导体生产的劳动力短缺问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/us-to-fight-labor-shortage-with-new-chips-act-worker-program</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 23:43:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星工会计划罢工三天 要求提高工资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/samsung-electronics-labor-union-to-stage-three-day-strike</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司最大的工会表示，将从 7 月 8 日开始举行为期三天的罢工，这给这家韩国最大公司在试图从半导体业务的挫折中恢复的过程中带来了更多挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-01/samsung-electronics-labor-union-to-stage-three-day-strike</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Jul 2024 15:04:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
